Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.94,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Remaining time until Prime\NMinister Fujiwara's public execution"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:50.53,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is there no final{\i}\N{\i1}piece to unravel this puzzle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:57.82,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wander around the search area with dread{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:05.37,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With shaky self-confidence{\i}\N{\i1}facing unyielding damnation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:09.21,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still alive, but I can't catch up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:15.43,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to residual images of hidden memories{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:19.64,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let loose dark shame unbounded{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.43,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the ends of this world of kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:27.52,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even hopes best forgotten are silenced{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.23,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as corruption spreads out before our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.44,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Consign it to darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:38.11,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ego on trial{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:49.29,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a moment of hesitation is seen ecstasy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\be6\an8}"Episode 11 '50,000 Hostages'"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been another blast.\NThis one was in Kinshicho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just as the warning told,\N- Kanda, any word from Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- explosions are starting\Nall over the country.\N- Kanda, any word from Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Eden's information was no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, there have been\Nmultiple bombings all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are outside,\Nplease avoid areas of heavy traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and return home quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many of them did he plant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could at least\Nfind out where the bombs are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we could send the bomb\Ndisposal squad out to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! There's a freaking\Nhuge number of bombs planted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you know where they are,\Nthey're in 1500 locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible to\Ndispose of them all in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The people\Nhave no choice but to wait in terror
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for their destruction to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as yearn for the\Njustice of the Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! There was a blast\Nat the Kidake-gumi's building!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kisugi-gumi is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you gotten through to\NSakura's cell phone yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling her again and\Nagain, but nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter's cell phone\NGPS data just came in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:41.99,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1 new message arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.28,Default - Style 00,,720,0,0,,{\an7}"From: Adam's Friend"\N\N"Subj:  'Bomb Locations'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomb locations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sakura is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuke, contact all the\Nbosses across the country! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.88,Default - Style 00,,720,0,0,,{\an7}"From: Adam's Friend"\N\N"Subj: 'Bomb Locations'"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is sending these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Track down the signal source!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right,\Nboth the maps, and the images!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Tower, the Tsutenkaku Tower,\Nthe Sapporo TVTower, Sky Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,check them all out! It's a facility
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that can transmit a signal to a wide area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't overlook\Nany relay stations, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this from Sky Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been up there, for an inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The roof had a place\Nlike this, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, it's possible that the\NPrime Minister is at Sky Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're ordering us to head\Nthere to rescue him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.87,Default - Style 00,,552,0,0,,{\an7}"From: Adam's Friend"\N\N"Subj: Prime Minister at Sky Tower"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who this is,\Nbut it appears he's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi and that Heike jerk\Nare there for sure, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The great Toki is gonna kick their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanda, contact Ogami, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud, Ogami {\i1}would{\i}\Ngo running off on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Number four, you go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do something about these bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. There's a whole mess of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and there may not be time\Nto disable them all individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do, that many more people will get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you handle it, "Number three"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go selling "the Great Yuki's"\Nsound special ability short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this show on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're checking to make sure\Nthere are no intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's most helpful, Heike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an honor to be of service, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure brings me back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Being here with you reminds\Nme of when we fought side by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,together as Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you're\Ntaking him yourself, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The last time, Ogami\Nwas just coming out of being Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Ogami's total power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Still the same old Ace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I will secure the perimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure no one\Ninterferes with your fight, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurakoji, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that you knew where we were, Ogami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wandered around\Nhere and there, last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I even went to the riverbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I searched all of the places\Nwhere we'd spent time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one after another. To think\Nthat you'd be {\i1}here,{\i} though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You did say that once\Nthis place was completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people would come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with their families, and girlfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Ironic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to come here\Nunder peaceful circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, you have to stop the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to\Ncontact Toki and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It got ruined when\NI was fighting Heike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I can\Nspeak to you for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,without anyone interrupting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me how to stop the blasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way killing people is okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it is to protect\Nthose with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, what you are doing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You almost sound like\Na champion of justice, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not justice. I am an evil,\Nwho has killed many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you how to stop the blasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I will defeat you,\Nand force it out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye; a tooth for a tooth;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,evil for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You take in the electricity with\Nthe {\i1}katana,{\i} avoiding the shocks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, with the conductive\Nproperties of your flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you release the electricity into the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's smart thinking, Ogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't be able to beat me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're attacked from\Nmultiple directions at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your flames can't redirect all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, if it weren't for this rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppy, chew through the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the way it's going to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hanging in there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not, by any chance,\Nexpecting me to go Lost, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you're more\Nlikely to go Lost before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you could be burnt up\Nby my electric shocks before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you don't want to\Nget killed, give yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you {\i1}will{\i} end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Swearing your allegiance to\Nthe Code: Breakers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...why did you try to\Nassassinate the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so {\i1}that's{\i} how the\Nstory is being sold, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I went there to discuss things with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was rejected by the Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I ended up being pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When he saw that I wouldn't back down...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was suddenly set upon, by some agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that\NI had to kill the agents
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process of escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, word that you\Nattacked the Prime Minister...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's false information, sent out by Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They made me out to be the villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and expelled me from the Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my demand was something\Nthey absolutely could not accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Code: Breakers\Nlive as people within society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that the\Nexistence of Code: Breakers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes known to the rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that happens,\Nthe world might become panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eden was afraid of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up as someone who\Nwas being pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to change Eden now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all I can do is apply\Npressure from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, for you\Nto do it by these means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an awful thing, to be sure.\NBut there is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this only out of\Nconsideration for Code: Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking the\Nchildren with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The country has been\Nisolating those with special abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and using them as research subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have high capabilities\Nwere recruited as Code: Breakers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but that just meant that\Nthey were the state's dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who carried out their killing for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they are\Noverseen by the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,those who have special\Nabilities have no freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Code: Breakers\Nlike you, Ogami, or Toki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that I want to save,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but everyone who will ever be born\Nwho possesses a special ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that you are thinking\Nabout those with special abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If children like Chisa are\Ngoing to meet a fate like she did,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then I feel the same way\Nabout wanting to make the world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,such that they can live here happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't right to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.37,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Emergency Alert"\N"...over 60 casualties. 6 explosions across Tokyo,\Nwith over 200 fatalities. 3 explosions in Kanagawa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only method\NI have remaining to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After the state has walked all over us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my grief over those who have\Ndied is something you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, you are correct.\NPerhaps I cannot understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, how can\Nyou do something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To the people you once tried to protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because those people are\Nnot worthy of being protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a man flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take out as many as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.39,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Welcome to Sky Tower"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The elevators are still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hitomi is sending out\Nelectrical signals across Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then he's in the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you here for, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I'm here to kick\NHitomi's ass, and stop the bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you mean, you really\Nhave turned traitor on us, Heike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing the job I'm\Nsupposed to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is killing people with bombs the\Njob of a Code: Breaker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always thought you\Nwere a bit of a dark horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it came to wiping out\Nevil as a Code: Breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I always felt you took pride in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, I never knew\Nyou thought so much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing I can do.\NI must... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what this means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that after I defeat you,\N{\i1}I'll{\i} be Code 02, won't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Heike! And now, farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For my sake, it's time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye! A tooth for a tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The hammer of justice for evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's Showtime" starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this, Toki and Heike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight Flush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Toki,\Nhow shall I bring you to pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sick sadistic bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a potty mouth.\NYou need to be spanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heike's Ten-Mirror-Flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My light information\Nis flawlessly copied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means my strength\Nand special abilities are also equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Toki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to\Nflatten me, and become Code 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After I kick your glittery little asses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna come and kick your ass directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your medicine, you sick pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are without beauty, Toki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But when compared to the speed of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki is using magnetism, and Heike\Nis using light power to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The people are not worthy of protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They are all fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! You're absolutely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The people are not fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Keep away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the Young Lady is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, all we can do is let\Nthe Young Lady take care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bomb over here.\NThere's no telling when it will go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are in danger, too, so stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, the police are taking action, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in Tokyo,\Nour Young Lady is giving her all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've gotta stick\Nour necks out, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dangerous area!\NPlease move to the park off of 3rd Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go looking down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think we do this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This area is dangerous!\NPlease move outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the bomb squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. There are too\Nmany places, and not enough men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who\Ndo all that they can for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they risk their\Nlives for the sake of those
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who are unworthy of\Nprotection, then they're fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why are they not worthy of protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Quickly, or the\Ntime for the explosion will arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the time comes,\Nthe Prime Minister will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, why are you trying\Nto save the Prime Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're a Code: Breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shaken up, Toki.\NAre you unsure of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you twinkling bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The people you protected...\Nthe people you tried to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...are now fools, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They're fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I accept you doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using quite a bit\Nof your special ability, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go Lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, the end is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Royal Straight Flu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure been on a spree, haven't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukihina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're finished now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm here, there's\Nno way you're getting through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come back from Hell for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:01.38,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you, too, will know{\i}\N{\i1}where that white crow is heading{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:07.01,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We fly through the brilliant city,{\i}\N{\i1}unnoticed by all around{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:21.52,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking only for a reason to live{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:26.99,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ashamed of our hollow selves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:31.74,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should we just laugh and go along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:37.37,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rules the world has decided on?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:42.13,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stripped bare, following{\i}\N{\i1}wherever our instincts lead{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:46.17,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the truth from{\i}\N{\i1}which we've averted our eyes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:50.80,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Verdicts handed down for no one's sake{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:55.64,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cast off the dark robes and get on your feet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:00.48,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure white wishes become our wings{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:05.15,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shake off your hesitations now, and fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:13.58,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have no fear; the answers{\i}\N{\i1}lie beyond the darkness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time,\N"Code: Breaker" episode 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Devils... God and Man...\NSakura Watching Over."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to bring an\Nend to all of this, Hitomi!
